# CODEOWNERS
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global ownership — all files require a review from a core maintainer
*                   @stellarbuild/maintainers

# Source code — requires SDK reviewer
/src/               @stellarbuild/sdk-reviewers

# Documentation — can be reviewed by docs team
/docs/              @stellarbuild/docs-reviewers
*.md                @stellarbuild/docs-reviewers

# CI/CD — requires DevOps sign-off
/.github/           @stellarbuild/devops

# Package configuration — requires maintainer approval
package.json        @stellarbuild/maintainers
tsconfig*.json      @stellarbuild/maintainers
